select-user-type.who_you_are: Tera ngkoe? (ko kona ni bitia imwina)
request-phone.type_your_phone: Taiaoka karina nambwan am tareboon. Ti aki kanakoa am nambwa n akean am kariaia.
request-phone.all_set: 👌 E a nako te kai, ko a konaa n ootana baom!
passenger-index.error_only_known_type: Ti rawata iroum, rinea te rebwerebwe, te kaa ke Settings.
passenger-request-location.provide_locat: Taiaoka Share am location (ke taibina am address) aonga n reke Turaiwa aika a uakaan.
passenger-request-destination.provide_de: Ko na nakea? Korea aran am tabo (e aonga n ataia te GPS) ke kabwarabwaraa.
order-submitted.order_submitted: ⏳ Ae tia kakaea baom... Ngkana e a reke baom, click te button inano 👇
order-cancelled.order_cancelled: 👌 Ko rabwa, e a toki kakaean am Turaiwa.
driver-select-vehicle-type.error_only_kn: Akea ngaira, taiaoka rinea Te Kaa ke Te Rebwerebwe.
driver-explain-checkins.text: E a kan tia. Tabeua bwaai: Telegram e aki kabongana te GPS ae maiu, ko na riai n check-in ni katoa tai e bitaki am tabo. Aio e na buokiira ni kakaea am Bwatintia aika a uakaan. Click "Next".
driver-request-location.provide_location: Taiaoka Share am location (press the button) ke taibina am tabo, ko aonga n reke irouia Bwatintia.
driver-explain-whats-next.text: E a nako te kai! Ko a kaongoaki ngkana iai Bwatintia ni uakaan. Tai tiringa te app aio. Click "Next".
driver-mute.mute_ok: ⚠️ Uringa ngkanne bwa ko a AKI kona n nooria Bwatintia irarikim ni karokoa ko Unmute.
driver-unmute.unmute_ok: Ko a Unmute ngkai a nang manga kaoti Bwatintia irarikim.
driver-checkin.provide_location: Taiaoka Share am location (press the button) ke taibina am tabo, ko aonga n reke irouia Bwatintia.
driver-checkin.ok: 👌 E rabwa te Check-in! Tuoa am location ieta, ngkana e bure, manga Check-in riki ao tap te paperclip-location (instead of pressing a button).
driver-order-new.distance: Raroam ma te Bwatintia: ~%s. A na tabo te bwatintia (click n zoom):
driver-order-new.price: Te bwatintia e tauraoi ni kabwaka: %s (te mwane)
driver-order-new.price_not_set: Akea a na boo te bwatintia. Ko a katea am boo.
passenger-request-price.set_price: N te app aio ao te bwatintia ae katea te boo 😉 Anganiira am boo. Iraua boon kantokam? (ke taibina "0" (zero) ngkana ko aki ataia)
passenger-request-price.should_be_numeri: Eik, e na riai n tii te nambwa! N aron aio: "50". Taiaoka kataia riki!
passenger-request-price.on_timeout: Ko a kaawa, ti nooria ae ko a rang maan n tataninga? Kabwara buren aio. Ngkana e tuai reke baom, ti a butiiko bwa ko a kataia riki rimwi. Ko rabwa riki n am taotaonaki n nano.
passenger-contact-new-number.message: 🔔 E butimwaea am boo {{driver}} ! Raroam ma te Turaiwa ~{{distance}}. Taiaoka tareboonia te turaiwa ni kamatoa am Order:
driver-order-set-price.set_price: Katea am boo. Ko kona ni kabwarabwaraa. N aron aio: "5, e rang buakaka te kootiweei" ke "10, e a boobuaka boon te bwa"
passenger-contact-driver-price.message: 🔔 ⚠️ {{driver}} e katea a na kantoka aio: "{{price}}". Raroam ma te Turaiwa ~{{distance}}. Ngkana ko kukurei, ko a tarebooniia ni kamatoa am Order:
passenger-verify-location.verify_locatio: Taiaoka noora te mabe ieta (click n zoom), eti am location aio?
passenger-verify-location.try_with_paper: Taiaoka kanakoa riki am location by clicking on paperclip, ao imwiina te location icon.
passenger-verify-cash.verify_cash: E tii butimwaeaki te mwane. Iai kantokam iroum?
passenger-verify-cash.get_some_cash: 🙁 Te kabwara bure, e riai ni iai kantokam. Kakaea moa angan am tianti ao ko a manga kataira imwiina!
driver-request-radius.request_radius: Kanga e na raroara am bwantintia aika ko kona n anaiia? Rineia inano 👇 ke taibina am raroa (10 km tokim ieta).
driver-request-radius.should_be_valid: E bure am rinerine. Rineia riki 👇 ke karina marenan 1 nakon 10.
global.default_options_message: Rinea nanom man te menu inano 👇
global.default_inline_options_message: Click te button 👇 ke ignore te message aio
global.replied_to_order: ✔️ E a nako te order aio☝️. Kantaninga am tareboon mai iroun am Bwatintia ni kamatoaa mwanangana.
global.error_try_again: Eik, ti a manga aki ota iroum. Taiaoka kataia riki.
global.error_location: Eik, ti a aki ataa am location anne. Taiaoka click te button ke kabonganaa te paperclip-location n kanakoa am GPS coordinates.
